snippet.title: Twinsanity: Trapped in Time - Reveal Trailer | PC
snippet.description:
Twinsanity: Trapped in Time is an upcoming RPG game, based on "Twinsanity The Animated Series". This will be the first game developed by Twinsanity's Channel. Enjoy this trailer. If you like this video press the "Like" button and subscribe my channel for more videos.

Link to the game:
https://gamejolt.com/games/twinsanity_trapped_in_time/396955
